node.text: @aceoftarot thank you! It is sad to see the backlash of asking to be a basic decent human being. One of the positive benefits of social media is putting out information we don't get to see, hear or know of in mainstream media.
@thecomptoncollective All true! Thanks again for your work 💕

Terry Crew's has been advocating for holding men accountable for a while now. I was in real shock hearing he too was molested and how other men laughed at him. This has been going on far too long. I truly hope this starts a whole new wave of real and raw issues of emotions, love and respect. When you understand the difference between masculinity and toxic-masculinity, you'll find yourself in better company, opportunities and blessings. You'll see you'll be real man of honor for yourself and for your family. Finally, marketing done right! @gillette Please make @kaepernick7, our modern MLKjr your ambassador, it will really piss off "real men"

#Patriarchy #ShaveWithGillete #ShedOldWays #TheBestMenCanBe #ToxicMasculinity #MenToo

This is the problem in our community a big problem as well as colorism it needs to stop period if we came together can u imagine the the things we could do..what ever happened to together we stand divided we fall
@theinfamousmissbruce isn't it amazing. I can't wait to see what will come of this
@thecomptoncollective hopefully a shift in behavior and the realization that gender is not an excuse for moronic actions

@crod_writer It really has me dumbfounded! But it just shows how installed we have these immoral values. Men feel as tough we are castrating them when all we want is to end bullying. It's baffling, but also good to know who to stay away from and whom I'll be supporting. I had a guy dm, asking for explanation... of what? It's EXHAUSTING to have to do work for and with them, it shows Neanderthals still live among us 😆😢🤮

Can you believe the huge backlash this received? This is advocating for respecting women, not bullying other boys/people and some men felt it was disrespectful. I’m like 🤷🏽‍♂️ what values do you uphold then?

@aceoftarot thank you! It is sad to see the backlash of asking to be a basic decent human being. One of the positive benefits of social media is putting out information we don't get to see, hear or know of in mainstream media.

Thank you for sharing all this - I don’t watch much tv and basically live under a rock 😆 so I hadn’t seen this ad, only heard some references to the backlash that I hadn’t followed up on. This commercial and the smart replies to the backlash has me in tears today. God bless Terry Crews and everyone working on this campaign and those who support it. These people are rays of hope! And so are you, for the work you are doing. 💕🙏🏻🌅
